sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant HTML as pdf-chunker.html
    participant Lambda as Lambda Function
    participant PyPDF2 as PyPDF2 Library
    
    User->>Browser: Opens website
    Browser->>HTML: Loads from S3
    HTML->>Browser: Displays upload interface
    
    User->>Browser: Drags PDF file
    Browser->>HTML: File selected
    
    HTML->>HTML: Validate (size, type)
    HTML->>HTML: Convert to Base64
    
    HTML->>Lambda: POST request with Base64 PDF
    
    Lambda->>Lambda: Check rate limit
    
    alt Rate limit exceeded
        Lambda->>HTML: 429 Error
        HTML->>Browser: Show "Rate limit exceeded"
    else Rate limit OK
        Lambda->>Lambda: Decode Base64
        Lambda->>PyPDF2: Extract text from PDF
        PyPDF2->>Lambda: Raw text
        
        Lambda->>Lambda: Clean formatting
        Lambda->>Lambda: Split into 20k chunks
        
        Lambda->>HTML: JSON response with chunks
        HTML->>Browser: Display chunks
        
        User->>Browser: Clicks "Copy to Clipboard"
        Browser->>User: Chunk copied!
        
        User->>Browser: Clicks "Download"
        Browser->>User: .txt file downloaded
    end
